Pania experienced some kind of wave bottom just two months after Jokow’s inauguration in October.
Eleven children were singing Christmas songs by a fire in Enarotal on December 7, 2014, when two Indonesian soldiers on motorcycles came out of the dark.
The frightened children told the soldiers that they should use headlights.
